parameters:
The exploration of this Great Hole has hardly progressed.
There are troublesome monsters placed to defend it.... If we
don't call for reinforcements... Hmm...

It's like looking at the Gate of Hell. How on earth did a
hole like this appear...

Are we going down here? Seriously...? I was scared and ran
back...

The monster inside the hole... Somehow, I feel like
something is off. I can't quite put my finger on it...

There's something strange about this place. It's like
something is off or, it's as if it doesn't belong in this
world...

I've never seen such a big hole before... It feels like I
could be sucked in if I peek...

There should have been an altar here that worshipped the
Earth Spirit... But suddenly, there's this huge hole...!

There could be a reason why the groundwater is decreasing,
causing these huge holes to appear... But I wonder where the
underground water veins are around here... Hmmm...

Oh, welcome. I'm happy that humans give me various
offerings... but, you see, I'm a teetotaler and a
vegetarian...  Note: The terms teetotaler and vegetarian are
used as is in Japanese, so I have kept them in English for
clarity.

Ah, should we proceed further? It seems like we can't make a
bonfire for some reason, so it might be a good idea to bring
plenty of healing items with us.

\SE[16]I'm the business trip Cat-chan~. \!\SE[10]Do you need
any items or anything!?\. (It's not free though!)

We're spirits, nice to meet you!! Our abs are ripped and
super cool...!!
